{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/65gve18v","slide":1,"text":"Building is becoming\nabundant.","textPreview":"Building is becoming | abundant.","textChars":30,"textLines":2,"bbox":[68,170,1000,160]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/76pcnmpg","slide":1,"text":"Attention is not.","textPreview":"Attention is not.","textChars":17,"textLines":1,"bbox":[68,360,700,88]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/87ydgrq1","slide":1,"text":"OPENAI BUILD WEEK  ·  HYDERABAD","textPreview":"OPENAI BUILD WEEK  ·  HYDERABAD","textChars":31,"textLines":1,"bbox":[68,646,450,20]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/t87upw7m","slide":1,"bbox":[1132,604,84,84]}
{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/dt28u0","slide":1,"text":"AI is making software easier to build than ever. But that changes what is scarce. When anyone can build, attention is the bottleneck."}
{"kind":"slide","id":"sl/j6lpyr","slide":2,"title":"W","textShapes":12}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/7a9wful0","slide":2,"bbox":[64,42,28,28]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/sbixoz2l","slide":2,"text":"W","textPreview":"W","textChars":1,"textLines":1,"bbox":[64,45,28,20]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/tcbeh436","slide":2,"text":"Workprint","textPreview":"Workprint","textChars":9,"textLines":1,"bbox":[104,43,160,24]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/udkfqpkr","slide":2,"text":"For builders before they\nare known, visibility matters.","textPreview":"For builders before they | are known, visibility matters.","textChars":55,"textLines":2,"bbox":[68,124,900,142]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/fetwjulc","slide":2,"bbox":[68,314,1144,2]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/gf2xsz2x","slide":2,"text":"01","textPreview":"01","textChars":2,"textLines":1,"bbox":[68,362,80,26]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/hgbel43i","slide":2,"text":"Feedback\nbefore launch.","textPreview":"Feedback | before launch.","textChars":23,"textLines":2,"bbox":[68,403,235,80]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/2hkfu9k3","slide":2,"text":"02","textPreview":"02","textChars":2,"textLines":1,"bbox":[354,362,80,26]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/3itwnel8","slide":2,"text":"Trust\nbefore purchase.","textPreview":"Trust | before purchase.","textChars":22,"textLines":2,"bbox":[354,403,235,80]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/ryhw3y1s","slide":2,"text":"03","textPreview":"03","textChars":2,"textLines":1,"bbox":[640,362,80,26]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/qx8vat07","slide":2,"text":"Proof\nbefore credentials.","textPreview":"Proof | before credentials.","textChars":25,"textLines":2,"bbox":[640,403,235,80]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/d0ze58jy","slide":2,"text":"04","textPreview":"04","textChars":2,"textLines":1,"bbox":[926,362,80,26]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/szqdc3id","slide":2,"text":"Relationships\nbefore they need them.","textPreview":"Relationships | before they need them.","textChars":36,"textLines":2,"bbox":[926,403,235,80]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/3axwzy1g","slide":2,"text":"Building in public lets you build the product and the audience at the same time.","textPreview":"Building in public lets you build the product and the audience at the same time.","textChars":80,"textLines":1,"bbox":[68,598,1060,36]}
{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/j6lpyr","slide":2,"text":"For early-stage founders, indie hackers and ambitious students, building in public means feedback before launch, trust before purchase, proof before credentials, and relationships before they need them."}
{"kind":"slide","id":"sl/rcfblq","slide":3,"title":"W","textShapes":8}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/elcjihcz","slide":3,"bbox":[64,42,28,28]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/1o32dwva","slide":3,"text":"W","textPreview":"W","textChars":1,"textLines":1,"bbox":[64,45,28,20]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/0nu1krup","slide":3,"text":"Workprint","textPreview":"Workprint","textChars":9,"textLines":1,"bbox":[104,43,160,24]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/ry1k7md8","slide":3,"text":"But building in public\nbecomes another job.","textPreview":"But building in public | becomes another job.","textChars":43,"textLines":2,"bbox":[68,125,900,144]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/qxsjehcn","slide":3,"text":"Decide what matters.","textPreview":"Decide what matters.","textChars":20,"textLines":1,"bbox":[102,350,600,32]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/d0j29wve","slide":3,"bbox":[68,365,18,2]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/sza1grut","slide":3,"text":"Find the story.","textPreview":"Find the story.","textChars":15,"textLines":1,"bbox":[102,410,600,32]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/3u1k32dc","slide":3,"bbox":[68,425,18,2]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/itsjaxcr","slide":3,"text":"Write the post.","textPreview":"Write the post.","textChars":15,"textLines":1,"bbox":[102,470,600,32]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/grmpcfut","slide":3,"bbox":[68,485,18,2]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/1cvq5kve","slide":3,"text":"Do it again tomorrow.","textPreview":"Do it again tomorrow.","textChars":21,"textLines":1,"bbox":[102,530,600,32]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/epk7apcn","slide":3,"bbox":[68,545,18,2]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/fqt83ad8","slide":3,"text":"while you are trying to ship the actual product.","textPreview":"while you are trying to ship the actual product.","textChars":48,"textLines":1,"bbox":[786,510,350,74]}
{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/rcfblq","slide":3,"text":"But it becomes another job: decide what matters, find the story, write the post, and do it again tomorrow while you are trying to ship the actual product."}
{"kind":"slide","id":"sl/dcekta","slide":4,"title":"W","textShapes":6}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/svex83e1","slide":4,"bbox":[64,42,28,28]}
