{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/6twf6dwv","slide":4,"text":"Workprint","textPreview":"Workprint","textChars":9,"textLines":1,"bbox":[104,43,160,24]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/58nex8fq","slide":4,"text":"Today, every\ndeveloper gets a\ncommunications team.","textPreview":"Today, every | developer gets a | communications team.","textChars":50,"textLines":3,"bbox":[68,152,835,215]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/47ux43e5","slide":4,"text":"Workprint","textPreview":"Workprint","textChars":9,"textLines":1,"bbox":[68,483,280,42]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/j6lwvyxk","slide":4,"text":"Your AI communications team for building in public.","textPreview":"Your AI communications team for building in public.","textChars":51,"textLines":1,"bbox":[68,535,590,36]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/i5cf2twz","slide":4,"bbox":[982,194,172,172]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/p47y9sfu","slide":4,"text":"W","textPreview":"W","textChars":1,"textLines":1,"bbox":[982,236,172,96]}
{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/dcekta","slide":4,"text":"So we asked: what if every developer had a communications team? This is Workprint: your AI communications team for building in public."}
{"kind":"slide","id":"sl/qypl95","slide":5,"title":"W","textShapes":7}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/6lo7ap8j","slide":5,"bbox":[64,42,28,28]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/t8f6l47u","slide":5,"text":"W","textPreview":"W","textChars":1,"textLines":1,"bbox":[64,45,28,20]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/876pczqp","slide":5,"text":"Workprint","textPreview":"Workprint","textChars":9,"textLines":1,"bbox":[104,43,160,24]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/jidofups","slide":5,"text":"It finds the story\nhiding in the work.","textPreview":"It finds the story | hiding in the work.","textChars":38,"textLines":2,"bbox":[68,112,570,130]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/yh4n6p87","slide":5,"text":"GitHub history  ·  Codex sessions  ·  progress","textPreview":"GitHub history  ·  Codex sessions  ·  progress","textChars":46,"textLines":1,"bbox":[68,270,520,26]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/kjm58zqd","slide":5,"text":"Not ‘we added browser automation.’","textPreview":"Not ‘we added browser automation.’","textChars":34,"textLines":1,"bbox":[68,385,530,34]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/bedobapw","slide":5,"text":"“AI assistants look intelligent\nuntil you ask them to complete\nan ordinary, messy task.”","textPreview":"“AI assistants look intelligent | until you ask them to complete | an ordinary, messy task.”","textChars":88,"textLines":3,"bbox":[68,432,535,118]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/ad4n258b","slide":5,"text":"A story people care about—already grounded in the work.","textPreview":"A story people care about—already grounded in the work.","textChars":55,"textLines":1,"bbox":[68,620,540,30]}
{"kind":"image","id":"im/krmx4je9","slide":5,"name":"","geometry":"roundRect","alt":"Workprint Story Inbox","bbox":[676,92,536,501]}
{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/qypl95","slide":5,"text":"Workprint looks at GitHub history, Codex sessions and project progress. It finds a moment worth sharing. Instead of ‘we added browser automation,’ it finds the real story: AI assistants look intelligent until you ask them to complete an ordinary, messy task."}
{"kind":"slide","id":"sl/p4rz13","slide":6,"title":"W","textShapes":7}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/atwja1cn","slide":6,"bbox":[64,42,28,28]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/xw72lgve","slide":6,"text":"W","textPreview":"W","textChars":1,"textLines":1,"bbox":[64,45,28,20]}
