{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/zypkn6dk","slide":6,"text":"Build the product.","textPreview":"Build the product.","textChars":18,"textLines":1,"bbox":[68,172,1050,78]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/yxg3elcz","slide":6,"text":"Build the audience.","textPreview":"Build the audience.","textChars":19,"textLines":1,"bbox":[68,260,1050,78]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/l072pgva","slide":6,"text":"From the same work.","textPreview":"From the same work.","textChars":19,"textLines":1,"bbox":[68,348,800,78]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/kzylgbu5","slide":6,"bbox":[68,500,240,3]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/72pkrqdg","slide":6,"text":"Workprint handles the archaeology and first draft.\nYou bring the judgment.","textPreview":"Workprint handles the archaeology and first draft. | You bring the judgment.","textChars":74,"textLines":2,"bbox":[68,535,700,56]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/m1g3ilcv","slide":6,"text":"workprint","textPreview":"workprint","textChars":9,"textLines":1,"bbox":[1050,650,166,20]}
{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/p4rz13","slide":6,"text":"Workprint does not manufacture content or pretend to be your voice. It handles the archaeology and first draft. You bring the judgment. Builders should not have to choose between building their product and building the audience that will make it matter."}